flowchart TD
    A[一次 run] --> B[Trace: 因果路径]
    A --> C[Log: 离散事件]
    A --> D[Metric: 聚合趋势]
    B --> E[trace_id / span_id]
    C --> F[event_name / severity / actor]
    D --> G[counter / histogram / gauge]
    E --> H[关联查询]
    F --> H
    G --> I[告警与 SLO]
    I --> H
    H --> J[事实 → 假设 → 处置]
    K[Audit: 谁基于何策略做了什么] --> H
